{"type": "article", "id": 31362, "title": "坐上摇椅，体验在鸟背上飞翔的感觉｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-23T23:28:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 16083, "name": "SHIFT"}, {"id": 31884, "name": "Sayar & Garibeh"}, {"id": 31885, "name": "ELKELAND Studio"}, {"id": 31886, "name": "NOMONO"}, {"id": 1526, "name": "Duffy London"}, {"id": 31887, "name": "FLOV Creative Agency"}, {"id": 31888, "name": "Damien Gerany"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 149, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160823230321nSwmYiQgE1yIK8xC.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Great Egret by Sayar &amp; Garibeh</h3><p>来自贝鲁特的 Sayar 和 Garibeh 是一对设计师情侣，他们成立的<a href=\"http://www.sayargaribeh.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">工作室</a>以大白鹭为灵感设计了这款与动物同名的摇椅 <a href=\"http://www.sayargaribeh.com/portfolio-item/great-egret/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Great Egret</a>。这把左右摇晃的椅子采用了一张像是巨翼的黑色坐垫，底部与黄铜组建相连，有一种简洁低调的风格。曲面的椅背将人包围起来，就像是坐在鸟背上飞翔一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230346krHPnd4WqxB7DSgE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230346MnyrwmYj9uQ8aJlo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230346omIHY5Ks4DzCRyfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230346msZ45Q6x2oDvugya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230346FfuUBYAWZJyHoVP3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608232303473iT69SX7aeMl1Rmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mer Noire by Damien Gerany</h3><p>大海一直以来都为设计师们提供了各式各样的灵感，之前我们就介绍过一套有着<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30289.html\">波纹表面的浴室家具</a>。这张由法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.damiengernay.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Damien Gernay</a> 打造 <a href=\"http://www.damiengernay.com/portfolio/mer-noire/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mer Noire</a> 的咖啡桌则利用黑色皮革将动感的海浪定格下来，在光线下很好地还原出了波光粼粼的感觉。因为深不可测的海洋而产生的恐惧感与纤薄的桌面形成了鲜明的对比，非常吸睛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230701cVHpMqtI7oFweXPJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655208\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230701CpmAbUlTKfOv7nJh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230701bDEjiw9I5uvUx7NX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230702ibVWSIu9Eaon4QUg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230701edwpsLzk02yPnNQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Surf-Ace Table + Bench by Duffy London</h3><p>当你第一眼看到英国制造商 <a href=\"https://duffylondon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Duffy London</a> 推出的 Surf-Ace 系列家具时，或许会折服于它自成一体的优雅弧度以及如同焦糖一样的木纹表面。它使用的木料均采自<a href=\"https://us.fsc.org/en-us\" rel=\"nofollow\">森林管理委员会</a>（<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forest_Stewardship_Council\" rel=\"nofollow\">Forest Stewardship Council</a>）认证的林区，然后利用一种和古时夏威夷人制作冲浪板相同的工艺打造出光滑弯曲的外形——Surf-Ace 这个名字也因此而来。这是它的<a href=\"https://duffylondon.com/product/tables/surface-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 18000 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230626adhFNjOSioBGktTb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230628AVF6sW9folInJCLr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608232306266W0w35uqyZBYa4CQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230626n5HeOVY1q2tamuFA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230627HeXMWZdvE7q1hRlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230627IWk0vVZjHCEm9erU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tabletop Mirrors by ELKELAND Studio</h3><p>在设计镜子这件事上，丹麦设计师 <a href=\"http://elkeland.bigcartel.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ida Elke</a> 想得不太一样：她希望自己的作品能够鼓励人们重新思考与镜像之间的互动，会在摆放这些精致的装饰品时进行一番思考。在创作了几何形挂镜 Mirror Mobile 系列之后，她在不久前举行的哥本哈根 <a href=\"http://www.northmodern.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">northmodern</a> 设计周上展出了有着异曲同工之妙的几款台式镜子。两片几何形的镜面通过黄铜杆连接在一起，可以根据需要摆放出不同的造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230550YHbOQE0LGUdPSsZq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230551Pw8SnTFmGr6tpqIJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230551L0qoHtCixQNsV4Xe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500795\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230551rhnTC69imKz8vMNy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608232305512u9Vw6T5ZMJWNzmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.493671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>U33 by Shift</h3><p>墨西哥设计工作室 <a href=\"http://byshift.mx/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shift</a> 最近推出了旗下第二款灯具 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41721897/U33\" rel=\"nofollow\">U33</a>，独立的吊灯模块之间经由灯罩外小小的亮黄色连接点相连。这种模块化设计允许用户打造出各式各样的组合，不仅实用更具有装饰效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230527ajUWnyRvSreFIJ9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.498571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230527nKk3mXMxw4YPhEpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230527pVsmcoXDMAPeNGbO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230528BNVWO2CHy1XE0auh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230528jr3po5JEken8UW4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608232305285S1JdqXo3L4cergi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Twój Browar by FLOV Creative Agency &amp; NOMONO</h3><p>波兰品牌 <a href=\"http://twojbrowar.pl/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twój Browar</a>（意思是“你的酿酒厂”）提供的服务和名字一样直白，专门出售为打算在自己家中酿酒或是制作奶酪的人所打造的必要工具。<a href=\"http://www.flov.co/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">FLOV Creative Agency</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.nomono.eu/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">NOMONO</a> 联手为它打造了一系列简洁的包装：设计师们对原本复杂而且庞大的酿酒设备进行了简化和缩小，保留了扭曲的管道和酿造锅等元素。这种对工艺的巧妙还原让人们能够一眼就将它与酿造和手工联系在一起，看起来非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230503aNqJTlwXZA4yYhpB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230506TMxUlC1m0uOZdi3e.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230508RL2K1NkefY5xQhST.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.927000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160823230508HOEcwWrnmQv9JTYh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}